segment.target: Juridisk repræsentation i Ukraine: Intellias Foundation for Change

segment.source: “My car was too good to sell, and I wish it a better destiny” – People express their motivation to donate a car in many ways, but they all share one wish.
segment.target: “Min bil var for god til at blive solgt, og jeg ønsker den en bedre skæbne" - Folk udtrykker deres motivation for at donere en bil på mange måder, men de deler alle et ønske.

segment.source: We source, upgrade and deliver cars to the frontlines in Ukraine.
segment.target: Vi indkøber, opgraderer og leverer biler til frontlinjen i Ukraine.

segment.source: Hundreds of people from every corner of the globe have bough for us, donated or sold their cars to give wheels to our warriors.
segment.target: Hundredvis af mennesker fra alle verdenshjørner har købt ind til os, doneret eller solgt deres biler for at give hjul til vores krigere.

segment.source: A car donation saves up to 75% of the cost, leaving only logistics, armoring, and maintenance to cover. More than half of the cars we deploy come as direct donations, and this number is growing. Check these incredible stories.
segment.target: En bildonation sparer op til 75 % af omkostningerne, så det kun er logistik, armering og vedligeholdelse, der skal dækkes. Mere end halvdelen af de biler, vi sender ud, kommer som direkte donationer, og det tal vokser. Se disse utrolige historier.

segment.source: Every story published brings us one step closer to our shared victory. Thank you!
segment.target: Hver historie, der offentliggøres, bringer os et skridt nærmere vores fælles sejr. Vi takker jer!

segment.source: All the achievements this project has wouldn’t be possible with people behind it.
segment.target: Alle de resultater, dette projekt har opnået, ville ikke være mulige uden mennesker bag det.

segment.source: People from from totally different industries like IT or logistics, education or media PR have united with a common mission and a common wish.
segment.target: Folk fra helt forskellige brancher som IT eller logistik, uddannelse eller medie-PR har forenet sig med en fælles mission og et fælles ønske.

segment.source: Since day 1 of the full scale invasion our warriors require mobility. Together with over 250 volunteers from all over the globe we are committed to serve our heroes and provide them 4x4 and other cars for as long as it takes.
segment.target: Siden dag 1 af den omfattende invasion har vores krigere haft brug for mobilitet. Sammen med over 250 frivillige fra hele verden er vi forpligtet til at tjene vores helte og give dem firehjulstrækkere og andre biler, så længe det er nødvendigt.

segment.source: Each car goes through a long process of logistics, armoring, and servicing before reaching the frontline."
segment.target: Hver bil gennemgår en lang proces med logistik, pansring og service, før den når frem til frontlinjen."

segment.source: Since 2022 we’ve been asking our soldiers what they need the most. Some need drones, other medical equipment, but the one common need for every unit no matter where they serve are reliable cars.
segment.target: Siden 2022 har vi spurgt vores soldater, hvad de har mest brug for. Nogle har brug for droner, andre medicinsk udstyr, men det eneste fælles behov for alle enheder, uanset hvor de gør tjeneste, er pålidelige biler.

segment.source: From every corner of the globe people come to Ukraine in person to stand with us and show their support.
segment.target: Fra alle verdenshjørner kommer folk personligt til Ukraine for at stå sammen med os og vise deres støtte.

segment.source: All the achievements this project has wouldn’t be possible without people behind it.
segment.target: Alle de resultater, dette projekt har, ville ikke være mulige uden menneskene bag det.

segment.source: People from totally different industries like IT or logistics, education or media PR have united with a common mission and a common wish.
segment.target: Folk fra helt forskellige brancher som IT eller logistik, uddannelse eller PR har samlet sig med en fælles mission og et fælles ønske.

segment.source: Since day 1 of the full-scale invasion, our warriors require mobility. Together with over 250 volunteers from all over the globe, we are committed to serving our heroes and providing them 4x4 and other cars for as long as it takes.
segment.target: Siden dag 1 af den fuldskala invasion har vores krigere haft brug for mobilitet. Sammen med over 250 frivillige fra hele verden er vi dedikeret til at støtte vores helte og levere dem 4x4-biler og andre køretøjer så længe det er nødvendigt.

segment.source: Dozens of people across EU, UK and the US have donated their cars or sold them to buy cars Ukrainian soldiers need right now.
segment.target: Dusinvis af mennesker over hele EU, Storbritannien og USA har doneret deres biler eller solgt dem for at købe biler, som ukrainske soldater har brug for lige nu.

segment.source: Dozens of people across EU, UK and the US have donated their cars or sold them to buy cars Ukrainian soldiers need right now.
segment.target: Dussintals människor över hela EU, Storbritannien och USA har donerat sina bilar eller sålt dem för att köpa bilar som ukrainska soldater behöver just nu.

segment.source: People who decide to donate a car and bring it to Ukraine in person not only provide a very tangible donationknowing exactly where and how the truck is used but also get a unique opportunity to meet with our team in Lviv,as well as spend some time in a gorgeous city of Lviv followed by a great dinner and some local beer 🙂
segment.target: Människor som bestämmer sig för att donera en bil och personligen ta den till Ukraina ger inte bara en mycket konkret donation och vet exakt var och hur lastbilen används utan får också en unik möjlighet att träffa vårt team i Lviv, samt tillbringa tid i den fantastiska staden Lviv följt av en härlig middag och lite lokal öl 🙂

segment.source: Want to Donate Car to Ukraine?
segment.target: Vill du donera bil till Ukraina?

segment.source: How would you like to help?
How can I donate my car to Ukraine?
segment.target: Hur kan jag donera min bil till Ukraina?

segment.source: You can donate car to Ukraine with us. Please fill up the form and we’ll get back to you within 24 hours. We focus mainly on pickup trucks and 4x4 cars, but other means of transportation such as vans, and civilian cars are accepted as soldiers also move around and have different tasks for which wheels are needed.
segment.target: Du kan donera bil till Ukraina genom oss. Fyll i formuläret så återkommer vi inom 24 timmar. Vi fokuserar främst på pickup-bilar och 4x4-bilar, men andra transportmedel som skåpbilar och personbilar accepteras också eftersom soldater rör sig och har olika uppgifter som kräver fordon.

segment.source: How to donate to Ukraine army?
segment.target: Hur kan jag donera till Ukrainas armé?

segment.source: You can donate to Ukraine army with Car for Ukraine, where we focus specifically on cars for the army. Pickup trucks, 4x4 cars, vans, etc. If you wish to donate your car, please fill up the form, and we’ll get back to you within 24 hours. To support the army financially, you can donate here supporting our initiative or check out Come Back Alive organization who helps Ukraine with various projects.
segment.target: Du kan donera till Ukrainas armé via Car for Ukraine, där vi fokuserar specifikt på bilar för armén. Pickup-bilar, 4x4-bilar, skåpbilar, etc. Om du vill donera din bil, fyll i formuläret så återkommer vi inom 24 timmar. För att ekonomiskt stödja armén kan du donera här och stödja vårt initiativ eller kolla på Come Back Alive-organisationen som hjälper Ukraina med olika projekt.

segment.source: How to donate a car to charity?
segment.target: Hur man donerar till Ukrainas armé?

segment.source: You can donate a car to charity with Car for Ukraine. We focus on providing the Ukrainian army with means of transportation which includes both lethal and humanitarian needs, such as evacuating people from war zones, bringing food and water, etc.
segment.target: Du kan donera en bil till välgörenhet med Car for Ukraine. Vi fokuserar på att förse den ukrainska armén med transportmedel som inkluderar både dödliga och humanitära behov, såsom att evakuera människor från krigszoner, föra mat och vatten etc.

segment.source: We focus on mobile combat groups who need 4-wheel drive diesel trucks with 2.0l engines or more. These are some of the best options: Toyota Hilux / Tundra, Mitsubishi L200, Ford Ranger, Nissan Navara/KingCab, Isuzu D-Max, Mazda BT-50 / Mazda B2500. Besides pickup trucks, 4x4 cars and vans as well as simple civilian vehicles are required too for various missions, e.g. aid delivery, food supplies, etc.
segment.target: Vi fokuserar på mobila stridsgrupper som behöver 4-hjulsdrivna diesellastbilar med 2,0 liters motorer eller mer. Dessa är några av de bästa alternativen: Toyota Hilux / Tundra, Mitsubishi L200, Ford Ranger, Nissan Navara/KingCab, Isuzu D-Max, Mazda BT-50 / Mazda B2500. Förutom pickuper krävs även 4x4-bilar och skåpbilar samt enkla civila fordon för olika uppdrag, t.ex. leverans av bistånd, matleveranser etc.

segment.source: Do I have to bring the car personally to Ukraine?
segment.target: Måste jag personligen ta med bilen till Ukraina?

segment.source: No, we can pickup your car anywhere in Europe or UK. But we’ll be also happy to assist you with all the paperwork if you decide to come in person.
segment.target: Nej, vi kan hämta din bil var som helst i Europa eller Storbritannien. Men vi hjälper dig också gärna med allt pappersarbete om du bestämmer dig för att komma personligen.
